Thank you, Firefox.

* Diana stopped in her tracks and looked back at Rion who was still by the 
monster, rolling her eyes and, ftupidly, ran back towards the monster and 
her friend.*

" RION! RUN!"

* But she ran up and past Rion, seeing monster jaws snap but dodged away 
just in time, swatting at it's lips before running in a different 
direction.*

" Come and get me! Neener, neener, neener!"
